ize your project using one of the following commands:\n- `npm init @shopify/app@latest` (installed by default with Node)\n- `pnpm create @shopify/create-app@latest`\n- `yarn create @shopify/app`\n- `bun create @shopify/app@latest` (experimental)\n\nLearn more in the docs: [Create an app](https://shopify.dev/apps/getting-started/create)\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n## Developing themes with Shopify CLI\n\nTo work with themes, the CLI needs to be installed globally with:\n\n- `npm install -g @shopify/cli @shopify/theme`\n\nYou can also use do it through Homebrew on macOS: `brew tap shopify/shopify && brew install shopify-cli`\n\nLearn more in the docs: [Shopify CLI for themes](https://shopify.dev/docs/themes/tools/cli)\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n## Developing Hydrogen custom storefronts with Shopify CLI ##\n\nThe Hydrogen code lives here: https://github.com/Shopify/hydrogen/tree/main/packages/cli\n\nLearn more in the docs: [Shopify CLI for Hydrogen storefronts](https://shopify.dev/docs/custom-storefronts/hydrogen/cli)\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n## Help 🖐\n\nIf you encounter issues using the CLI or have feedback you'd like to share with us, below are some options:\n\n- [Open a GitHub issue](https://github.com/Shopify/cli/issues) - To report bugs or request new features, open an issue in the Shopify CLI repository\n- [Shopify Community Forums](https://community.shopify.com/) - Visit our forums to connect with the community and learn more about Shopify CLI development\n- [CLI Documentation - Apps](https://shopify.dev/apps/tools/cli) - To view CLI documentation for app development\n- [CLI Documentation - Themes](https://shopify.dev/themes/tools/cli) - To view CLI documentation for theme development\n- [CLI Documentation - Hydrogen](https://shopify.dev/custom-storefronts/tools/cli) - To view CLI documentation for Hydrogen (custom storefront) development\n\n## Contribute 👩🏽‍💻\n\nIf you'd like to contribute to the project, check out the [contributors docs](/docs) and the [steps to get started](/docs/cli/get-started.md).\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n## References\n\n- [oclif](https://oclif.io/)\n","engines":{"node":">=14.17.0"},"private":false,"scripts":{"lint":"nx lint","test":"nx run theme:test","build":"nx build","clean":"nx clean","lint:fix":"nx lint:fix","test:watch":"nx test:watch","type-check":"nx type-check","schema:generate":"node scripts/schema/generate.js && pnpm nx lint:fix"},"_npmUser":{"name":"shopify-dep","email":"npmjs+shopify-dep@shopify.com"},"_resolved":"","_integrity":"","deprecated":"This package is deprecated. As of Shopify CLI version 3.59.0, it is bundled with @shopify/cli. Please use that package instead.","repository":{"url":"https://github.com/Shopify/cli/edit/main/packages/theme","type":"git"},"_npmVersion":"6.14.18","description":"Utilities for building and publishing themes","directories":{},"_nodeVersion":"16.13.2","dependencies":{"yaml":"2.3.2","@oclif/core":"2.11.7","@shopify/cli-kit":"0.0.0-nightly-20231109214326","@shopify/theme-check-node":"1.20.1","@shopify/theme-language-server-node":"1.5.1"},"eslintConfig":{"extends":["../../.eslintrc.cjs"]},"engine-strict":true,"publishConfig":{"access":"public","@shopify:registry":"https://registry.npmjs.org"},"_hasShrinkwrap":false,"readmeFilename":"README.md","devDependencies":{"vite":"^4.4.9","vitest":"^0.34.3","@types/node":"16.18.57","node-stream-zip":"^1.15.0","json-schema-to-zod":"0.6.3"},"_npmOperationalInternal":{"tmp":"tmp/theme_0.0.0-nightly-20231109214326_1699566312314_0.5149202544576279","host":"s3://npm-registry-packages"}},"0.0.0-experimental-20231110121607":{"name":"@shopify/theme","version":"0.0.0-experimental-20231110121607","license":"MIT","_id":"@shopify/theme@0.0.0-experimental-20231110121607","maintainers":[{"name":"jaimie.rockburn","email":"jaimie.rockburn@shopify.com"},{"name":"blittle","email":"bret.little@gmail.com"},{"name":"shopify-admin","email":"npmjs@shopify.com"},{"name":"maryharte","email":"mary.harte@shopify.com"},{"name":"crisfmb","email":"cristina.borges@shop